thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Colin Cassidy Media

author: Colin Cassidy Media
title: Colin Cassidy Media
text: Mark from the Sydney store just hasn't returned my calls, or emails for nearly a week. Equipment I purchased had a constant hum through it. I'm a working studio and need things resolved faster than Store DJ is working currently. Hope to hear from you soon guys. Not particularly happy Jan.
